        <productcategorycomponent product="{&#34;image&#34;:&#34;assets/images/800MT-TOURING_Twilight-Blue.png&#34;,&#34;title&#34;:&#34;800MT TOURING&#34;,&#34;desc&#34;:&#34;The road ahead is not always clearly defined. Down each path, and around every unknown bent, new discoveries await. Sometimes you don\u0027t know where to go, but you couldn\u0027t care less.\r\n\r\nImmerse in the free, intense adrenaline, strong emotions. Every day will be inspiring. The journey, its ultimately important thing is not where the end of the road is, but where your mind takes you.\r\n\r\nWith CFMOTO 800MT, it resets your compass.&#34;,&#34;specificationImage&#34;:&#34;assets/images/800MT_旅行版_左45.png&#34;,&#34;categoryButton&#34;:&#34;Download brochure&#34;,&#34;imageAreas&#34;:[{&#34;shape&#34;:&#34;circle&#34;,&#34;coords&#34;:&#34;420,465,26&#34;,&#34;altText&#34;:&#34;5&#34;},{&#34;shape&#34;:&#34;circle&#34;,&#34;coords&#34;:&#34;896,571,38&#34;,&#34;altText&#34;:&#34;4&#34;},{&#34;shape&#34;:&#34;circle&#34;,&#34;coords&#34;:&#34;770,176,29&#34;,&#34;altText&#34;:&#34;3&#34;},{&#34;shape&#34;:&#34;circle&#34;,&#34;coords&#34;:&#34;679,189,22&#34;,&#34;altText&#34;:&#34;2&#34;},{&#34;shape&#34;:&#34;circle&#34;,&#34;coords&#34;:&#34;551,488,30&#34;,&#34;altText&#34;:&#34;1&#34;}],&#34;imageRealWidth&#34;:1140,&#34;imageRealHeight&#34;:760}" image="assets/images/800MT-TOURING_Twilight-Blue.png" category="{&#34;title&#34;:&#34;800&#34;,&#34;button&#34;:&#34;Find a Distributor&#34;,&#34;link&#34;:&#34;/content/cfmoto/global/about-us/global_distributors&#34;,&#34;tips&#34;:&#34;CFMOTO models may have different specifications to comply with local regulations, and maybe modified to meet specific demands in a particular region.&#34;,&#34;downloadBrochureText&#34;:&#34;Download brochure&#34;,&#34;downloadBrochureLink&#34;:&#34;assets/images/documentation/2021_800MT brochure_International.pdf&#34;,&#34;downloadName&#34;:&#34;2021_800MT brochure_International.pdf&#34;,&#34;motorcycleType&#34;:&#34;MOTORCYCLE&#34;,&#34;pointData&#34;:[{&#34;name&#34;:&#34;dot-point0&#34;,&#34;des&#34;:&#34;Equipped with a bi-directional quickshifter, the rider only needs to use the clutch in the events of startup or parking. Making shifting through gears effortlessly and quick, allowing for a more focused riding experience&#34;,&#34;img&#34;:&#34;assets/images/关键部位图/20210816105733.png&#34;,&#34;number&#34;:&#34;/etc/designs/cfmoto/assets/product/category/01@2x.jpg&#34;},{&#34;name&#34;:&#34;dot-point1&#34;,&#34;des&#34;:&#34;When the speed is greater than 40km/h and the gear is above the 4th gear, the rider can switch on the cruise control and use the RES and SET buttons to increase or decrease the speed respectively. The maximum cruise speed is set to 120km/h. With the assistance of cruise control, the rider can maintain a fixed speed without applying the throttle. It reduces the rider&#39;s fatigue and makes touring more comfortable, moreover, it can reduce unnecessary speed change and enhance fuel efficiency&#34;,&#34;img&#34;:&#34;assets/images/关键部位图/20210816105842.png&#34;,&#34;number&#34;:&#34;/etc/designs/cfmoto/assets/product/category/02@2x.jpg&#34;},{&#34;name&#34;:&#34;dot-point2&#34;,&#34;des&#34;:&#34;The rider can check the tire pressure in the menu at any time when riding and detect any deviations in tire pressure promptly. The ride rcan also adjust the tire pressure to adapt to different terrains and enhance the passing capability&#34;,&#34;img&#34;:&#34;assets/images/关键部位图/20210816105829.png&#34;,&#34;number&#34;:&#34;/etc/designs/cfmoto/assets/product/category/03@2x.jpg&#34;},{&#34;name&#34;:&#34;dot-point3&#34;,&#34;des&#34;:&#34;The CFMOTO 800MT Touring is equipped with a cross-spoke rim,which has good impact resistance and reduces the wheel&#39;s weight During the journey, the spoke wheels can cope with harsher road conditions and are easier to repair in emergencies&#34;,&#34;img&#34;:&#34;assets/images/关键部位图/20210818090305.png&#34;,&#34;number&#34;:&#34;/etc/designs/cfmoto/assets/product/category/04@2x.jpg&#34;},{&#34;name&#34;:&#34;dot-point4&#34;,&#34;des&#34;:&#34;Uneven terrain is usually uncomfortable and can be rough on your suspension, causing sudden jolts and twists and possible damage.A stabilizer helps keep the motorcycle going straight over dicult terrains such as rocks or ruts and also smooths out jolts through the handlebars, thus reducing arm fatigue by minimizing the e ort tocontrol the handlebars.&#34;,&#34;img&#34;:&#34;assets/images/关键部位图/20210816105842.png&#34;,&#34;number&#34;:&#34;/etc/designs/cfmoto/assets/product/category/05@2x.jpg&#34;}]}" variant="[{&#34;image&#34;:&#34;assets/images/800MT-TOURING_Twilight-Blue.png&#34;,&#34;title&#34;:&#34;Twilight-Blue&#34;,&#34;desc&#34;:&#34;&#34;,&#34;modelColor&#34;:&#34;&#34;,&#34;colorImage&#34;:&#34;assets/images/Twilight Blue.png&#34;},{&#34;image&#34;:&#34;assets/images/800MT-TOURING_Sandstone-Yellow.png&#34;,&#34;title&#34;:&#34;Sandstone-Yellow&#34;,&#34;desc&#34;:&#34;&#34;,&#34;modelColor&#34;:&#34;&#34;,&#34;colorImage&#34;:&#34;assets/images/Sandstone Yellow.png&#34;}]"/>
