        <productgraphiccomponent config="{&#34;title&#34;:&#34;POWER &amp; LIGHTWEIGHT&#34;,&#34;description&#34;:&#34;799cc parallel twin-cylinder engine with a max. power of 70kw@9000rpm (95hp) and a max. torque of 77N.m@7500rpm.\r\nThe main frame and sub-frame together weigh only 16kg, and the high-strength cast aluminum alloy swingarm weighs only 6.9kg. With a curb weight of ≤231kg without luggage boxes, this bike is impressively light and agile.&#34;,&#34;pcTitleFontSize&#34;:&#34;&#34;,&#34;mobTitleFontSize&#34;:&#34;&#34;,&#34;pcDescFontSize&#34;:&#34;&#34;,&#34;mobDescFontSize&#34;:&#34;&#34;,&#34;fullScreenImage&#34;:&#34;assets/images/800MT TR_02.png&#34;,&#34;style&#34;:&#34;fullScreen&#34;,&#34;bottomDescClass&#34;:&#34;&#34;}"/>
