    <div class="product-graphic-component">
    <div class="product_graphic_component" data-component="product-graphic-component">
        <productgraphiccomponent config="{&#34;title&#34;:&#34;HANDLING&#34;,&#34;description&#34;:&#34;The 160mm KYB upside-down front suspension with adjustable preload, rebound, and damping (20 clicks) coupled with the 150mm KYB rear suspension with adjustable preload and rebound (20 clicks) provide a smooth ride even on uneven terrain.  J. Juan disc brakes with 320mm dual-disc radial caliper at the front and 260mm single-disc at rear offer reliable stopping power.  The cast aluminum wheels and Maxxis tubeless tires with a front size of 19\&#34; and rear size of 17\&#34; provide excellent traction.  The 190mm ground clearance further enhances the bike&#39;s ability to tackle rough terrain.  Additionally, a stabilizer helps keep the motorcycle stable and minimizes jolts through the handlebars, thus reducing arm fatigue during extended rides.&#34;,&#34;pcTitleFontSize&#34;:&#34;&#34;,&#34;mobTitleFontSize&#34;:&#34;&#34;,&#34;pcDescFontSize&#34;:&#34;&#34;,&#34;mobDescFontSize&#34;:&#34;&#34;,&#34;style&#34;:&#34;highlyAdaptive&#34;,&#34;bottomDescClass&#34;:&#34;&#34;}" adaptive="{&#34;imageList&#34;:[{&#34;image&#34;:&#34;assets/images/800MT TR_05.png&#34;},{&#34;image&#34;:&#34;assets/images/800MT TR_06.png&#34;},{&#34;image&#34;:&#34;assets/images/800MT TR_07.png&#34;}]}"/>
