    <div class="product-graphic-component">
    <div class="product_graphic_component" data-component="product-graphic-component">
        <productgraphiccomponent config="{&#34;title&#34;:&#34;RIDING EXPERIENCE&#34;,&#34;description&#34;:&#34;The selectable Sport/Rain modes conveniently located on the multi-function handlebar, can also be used to check the tire pressure from the menu, allowing riders to customize their experience according to their preferences and the road conditions.The Cornering ABS function adds an extra layer of safety and enjoyment, enabling riders to confidently navigate challenging terrains. For long-distance rides, the Cruise Control function provides a comfortable and effortless experience, allowing riders to maintain speeds up to 120 km/h.The two silver-colored aluminum cases with locks provide 63L of storage space,and top case has 6L of storage space.Keeping an eye on the motorcycle&#39;s performance is made effortless with the 7-inch full-color TFT display and multi-functional instrument panel.&#34;,&#34;pcTitleFontSize&#34;:&#34;&#34;,&#34;mobTitleFontSize&#34;:&#34;&#34;,&#34;pcDescFontSize&#34;:&#34;&#34;,&#34;mobDescFontSize&#34;:&#34;&#34;,&#34;style&#34;:&#34;fixedHeight&#34;,&#34;bottomDescClass&#34;:&#34;&#34;}" fixed="{&#34;imageList&#34;:[{&#34;desc&#34;:&#34;Sport/Rain modes&#34;,&#34;image&#34;:&#34;assets/images/800MT TR_08.png&#34;},{&#34;desc&#34;:&#34;Cornering ABS&#34;,&#34;image&#34;:&#34;assets/images/800MT TR_09.png&#34;},{&#34;desc&#34;:&#34;7-inch full-color TFT display&#34;,&#34;image&#34;:&#34;assets/images/800MT TR_10.png&#34;}]}"/>
